SUMMARY:Ask An Alumn @ Dinnovators
DESCRIPTION:Organized by: ['Center for Innovation and Leadership']\\nCatego
 ry: Meeting\\nCome Join us for Ask An Alumn with a guest alumn where you c
 an hear about his experience and ask questions followed by dinner hosted b
 y Dinnovators. This Swattie Alum is a user experience researcher and recov
 ering political scientist. His career is best described as an unplanned sc
 enic tour through the world of applied research with phases in finance\, i
 nsurance\, human resources\, and two hair-on-fire startups. Now in his civ
 ic tech era\, he works for a state government digital services team. He's 
 happy to field questions about careers in UX\, tech\, and government. Food
  will be provided including Vegan and Vegetarian options.\\nDetails: https
 ://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%3D135325
 2378
