 ies\, and trained as a cultural anthropologist from the University of Penn
 sylvania\, will be an honorarium guest speaker for this teach-in on The As
 ian Caribbean: Culture and History. \\nDetails: https://swatcentral.swart
 hmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%3D1370415908
