SUMMARY:CWP Writers' Week
DESCRIPTION:Organized by: ['English Literature']\\nCategory: Lecture/Panel 
 Discussion\\nJOIN US FOR SWARTHMORE'S BIENNIAL SPRING WRITING FESTIVAL! AL
 L READINGS BEGIN AT 4:30 PM\, FOLLOWED BY A BOOK GIVEAWAY.Tuesday - Angela
  Flournoy in the Scheuer Room. Noveslit Angela Flournoy reads from her wor
 k and announces the Fiction winners of the Annual Student Writing Contest!
  Tuesday - Sarah Yahm in the Scheuer Room. Featured alum Sarah Yahm prese
 nts her work and fields questions. Wednesday - Chet'la Sebree in the Sche
 uer Room. Poet Chet'la Sebree reads from her work and announces the Poetry
  winners of the Annual Student Writing Contest! Thursday- Angela Pelster-
 Wiebe in McCabe 104Essayist Angela Pelster-Wiebe presents her work and ann
 ounces the Non-fiction winners of the Annual Student Writing Contest!REFRE
 SHMENTS WILL BE SERVED!\\nDetails: https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?tru
 mbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%3D1342594567
