 uer Room. Poet Chet'la Sebree reads from her work and announces the Poetry
  winners of the Annual Student Writing Contest! Thursday- Angela Pelster-
 Wiebe in McCabe 104Essayist Angela Pelster-Wiebe presents her work and ann
 ounces the Non-fiction winners of the Annual Student Writing Contest!REFRE
