SUMMARY:SSQL Workshop: Exploring Data in R
DESCRIPTION:Organized by: ['Sociology and Anthropology'\, 'Economics'\, 'Po
 litical Science']\\nCategory: Training/Workshop\\nThis workshop will focus
  on how to explore andunderstand data in R. You will learn techniquesfor e
 xamining variables\, summarizing datasets\,and identifying patterns or pro
 blems in your databefore moving on to analysis. We will coverdescriptive s
 tatistics\, frequency tables\, handlingmissing values\, and strategies for
  cleaning andpreparing data.\\nDetails: https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu
 /?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%3D1357216278
