SUMMARY:Breathe in Bloom: Outdoor Stress Fest
DESCRIPTION:Organized by: ['SWELL Team'\, 'Be Well']\\nCategory: Student Ac
 tivity (no alcohol)\\nA fair to help students relax and take a break while
  simultaneously teaching them about practices they can use to de-stress in
  nature\, including coregulation education\, mandala making\, and outdoor 
 games. With therapy dogs\, picnic blankets\, fresh food\, and calm music\,
  this outdoor event will have no rigid order to it\; instead\, it will fol
 low more of a "festival" format with outdoor activities and nature-centere
 d stress education interwoven throughout.\\nDetails: https://swatcentral.s
 warthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%3D1379378869
LOCATION:Isabelle Cosby Courtyard
URL:https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%
 3D1379378869
CATEGORIES:Student Activity (no alcohol)
END:VEVENT
