  There will also be a poster session beginning at 2:15 pm in the Chang Hou
  Lobby and Eldridge Commons with participation by students from Swarthmore
 \, Haverford and Bryn Mawr Colleges.  Light refreshments will be served.
   Please contact Lauren Nuttle - lnuttle1@swarthmore.edu with any questi
