SUMMARY:Study Abroad 101
DESCRIPTION:Organized by: ['Global Engagement Office']\\nCategory: Meeting\
 \nAre you interested in studying abroad during the Spring 2027 Semester? P
 lanning should begin now. The GEO deadline to apply to study abroad in the
  Spring 2027 semester is June 1\, 2026. Your first step is to attend an GE
 O Study Abroad 101 Information Session. This session is the first GEO requ
 irement in the Swarthmore Approval for Study Abroad process. You will le
 arn essential information to consider while planning\, as well as next ste
 ps to choose and apply for programs\\nDetails: https://swatcentral.swarthm
 ore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%3D1370415911
LOCATION:McCabe Library Room 320-Video Classroom
URL:https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%
 3D1370415911
CATEGORIES:Meeting
END:VEVENT
