SUMMARY:Interfaith Lunch
DESCRIPTION:Organized by: ['Interfaith Center']\\nCategory: Reception\\nThe
  Interfaith Center warmly invites you to an Interfaith Lunch. We hope to b
 ring together all of our students\, religious affinity groups\, advisors\,
  and interns under one roof. We hope that this will be an evening of inter
 faith connection\, conversation\, and community building. We welcome stud
 ents and anyone interested in interfaith life on campus – whether or not
  you belong to a faith community.  Come share your stories\, ideas\, and 
 hopes for how we can learn from one another and work together in meaningfu
 l ways!\\nDetails: https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3D
 event%26eventid%3D1372874149
LOCATION:Hormel/Nguyen Intercultural Center at Sproul Hall Room 201 Dome Ro
 om
URL:https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%
 3D1372874149
CATEGORIES:Reception
END:VEVENT
