 he faculty and staff exclusive event taking place from 4:30-6pm.  This ev
 ent includes open house art galleries\, live student music ensembles\, bar
 s\, and karaoke.   pARTy is the annual open house event exhibiting Art\, 
 Architectural Studies\, and Art History's student’s artwork/projects. pA
 RTy immediately follows ARTini at 6pm welcoming students\, faculty and sta
 ff. This event includes open house art galleries\, live student music ense
 mbles\, food trucks\, beverage options for both the over and 21 crowds\, a
 nd karaoke.\\nDetails: https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=vie
