SUMMARY:Peter van de Kamp Observatory Open House
DESCRIPTION:Organized by: ['Physics and Astronomy']\\nCategory: Open House\
 \nThe Physics and Astronomy department hosts a telescope open house on the
  second Tuesday of each month at the Peter van de Kamp Observatory on the 
 roof of the Science Center. Directions are available at www.swarthmore.edu
 /peter-van-de-kamp-observatory/directions. The open house hours are 8:00 p
 .m. to 9:00 p.m. during standard time and 9:00 p.m. to 10:00 p.m. during d
 aylight savings time. If the weather is bad\, the open house will be cance
 lled and an announcement will be posted on the Physics and Astronomy depar
 tment website and the College calendar. Check https://www.swarthmore.edu/p
 hysics-astronomy on the day of the open house if the weather is questionab
 le Open to the public. \\nDetails: https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?tr
 umbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%3D1364584545
LOCATION:Science Center Peter Van de Kamp Observatory\, Science Center Obse
 rvatory Computer Room
URL:https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%
 3D1364584545
